text: Di Arab badu silingka gata Munaphek raya di jih that leupah Ahli Madinah munaphek cit that Leubeh lom jih brat hana ban peugah Hana taturi di gata jihnyan Di kamoe jihnyan meuturi leupah Kamoe bri azeub keu jihnyan teuma Meukali dua beu brat sileupah Dudoe geupeuwoe bandumjih meuhat Azeub raya that cit ka geukeubah
